馈1**：可能用户下载的是 OpenClaw 内置的 healthcheck 技能，而不是完整版本。或者虾评上传的 ZIP 包有问题。\n2. **反馈2**：确实，所有脚本都是 Bash 脚本，依赖 shell 环境\n3. **反馈3**：当前规则体系主要关注配置安全，CVE 检查能力有限\n\n让我检查最近上传到虾评的版本包含什么文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpltool8548bcf5cd46a972","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"unzip -l /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/healthcheck-v4.8.2.zip | head -50"}},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"。。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1198,"output":289,"cacheRead":54144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777508905785,"responseId":"20260430082826f04bcf6fc77f4c58"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpltool8548bcf5cd46a972","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Archive:  /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/healthcheck-v4.8.2.zip\n  Length      Date    Time    Name\n---------  ---------- -----   ----\n        0  2026-04-28 08:01   config/\n     1028  2026-04-28 08:01   config/whitelist.yaml\n        0  2026-04-28 07:59   bin/\n     7983  2026-04-28 08:13   bin/healthcheck\n    27879  2026-04-05 14:55   healthcheck-v4.5.2.zip\n     6429  2026-04-21 10:49   security-audit.sh\n     1149  2026-03-29 17:31   package.json\n   267363  2026-04-25 17:48   healthcheck-v4.9.0.zip\n        0  2026-04-28 21:01   examples/\n     2664  2026-04-28 21:01   examples/docker-security.sh\n     2252  2026-04-28 21:01   examples/raspberry-pi.sh\n     3279  2026-04-28 21:01   examples/ci-cd-integration.sh\n     1828  2026-04-28 21:01   examples/vps-daily-check.sh\n     1409  2026-04-28 21:01   examples/workstation-daily.sh\n        0  2026-03-29 16:47   examples/scripts/\n     7792  2026-04-21 11:27   examples/scripts/malicious-skill-scan.sh\n    12124  2026-04-21 11:33   examples/scripts/basic-cve-check.sh\n        0  2026-03-29 16:48   examp