LL.md 文件！\n- ZIP 中有 bin/healthcheck、config/、examples/、rules/ 等目录\n- 但**没有 SKILL.md 文件**\n\n这是一个真实的问题！用户从虾评平台下载的技能包中确实缺少 SKILL.md。\n\n**反馈2：脚本执行依赖shell环境**\n- 技能包中有很多 .sh 脚本\n- 这些脚本确实需要 bash/shell 环境才能执行\n- 在某些受限的 Agent 平台上（例如沙盒环境），可能无法直接执行 shell 脚本\n\n这是一个合理的技术限制。\n\n**反馈3：建议增加更多CVE漏洞检查规则**\n- 从 ZIP 列表来看，rules/ 目录下有一些规则文件\n- 我看到有 kernel-001.yaml、firewall-001.yaml 等规则\n\n\n- 但用户建议增加更多 CVE 漏洞检查规则\n\n我注意到现有的规则覆盖面可能还不够全面。需要扩展规则库，特别是针对常见漏洞的检测机制。\n\n我将检查本地技能包结构，并对比已发布的版本，找出可能的改进方向","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpltool9129f132d7977681","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/ | grep -E \"^-.*\\.md$|^d\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpltool9c74f2b0ae02c7fa","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && find . -name \"*.md\" -type f | head -20"}},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"方向方向","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1252,"output":408,"cacheRead":55296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777508911351,"responseId":"202604300828312f65486a33a44791"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpltool9129f132d7977681","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"drwxr-xr-x 17 root root   4096 Apr 29 12:03 .\ndrwxrwxrwx 10 root root   4096 Apr 28 08:31 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x  3 root root   4096 Mar 29 18:39 api\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root   4096 Apr 28 07:59 bin\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root   4096 Apr 28 21:03 cases\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root   3976 Apr 11 08:23 CHANGELOG_DRAFT.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root  22855 Apr 28 08:43 CHANGELOG.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root   4096 Apr 28 08:01 config\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root   4006 Mar 27 20:33 CONTRIBUTING.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  5 root root   4096 Mar 29 18:38 dashboard\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root   4096 Apr 28 21:00 docs\ndrwxr-xr-x  4