c web interaction.","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/workspace/skills/agent-browser/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/workspace/skills/agent-browser","source":"openclaw-workspace","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/workspace/skills/agent-browser","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/workspace/skills/agent-browser/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-workspace"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"coze-asr","name":"coze-asr","description":"Convert speech audio to text using Coze ASR. Use when you need to transcribe spoken content from a remote audio URL or a local audio file into plain text.","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-asr/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-asr","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-asr","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-asr/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"coze-image-gen","name":"coze-image-gen","description":"Generate one or more images from text prompts using Coze image generation. Use when you need to create images from a natural-language prompt, produce multiple image variants, or generate sequential frames from the same prompt.","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-image-gen/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-image-gen","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-image-gen","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-image-gen/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"coze-tts","name":"coze-tts","description":"Convert text to speech using Coze TTS. Use when you need to synthesize spoken audio from one text input or multiple text segments, optionally with a specific speaker, format, sample rate, or speech settings.","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-tts/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-tts","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-tts","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/coze-tts/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-bitable","name":"feishu-bitable","description":"飞书多维表格（Bitable）的创建、查询、编辑和管理工具。包含 27 种字段类型支持、高级筛选、批量操作和视图管理。\n\n**当以下情况时使用此 Skill**：\n(1) 需要创建或管理飞书多维表格 App\n(2) 需要在多维表格中新增、查询、修改、删除记录（行数据）\n(3) 需要管理字段（列）、视图、数据表\n(4) 用户提到\"多维表格\"、\"bitable\"、\"数据表\"、\"记录\"、\"字段\"\n(5) 需要批量导入数据或批量更新多维表格","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-bitable/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-bitable","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-bitable","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-bitable/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-calendar","name":"feishu-calendar","description":"飞书日历与日程管理工具集。包含日历管理、日程管理、参会人管理、忙闲查询。","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-calendar/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-calendar","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-calendar","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-calendar/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-channel-rules","name":"feishu-channel-rules","description":"Lark/Feishu channel output rules. Always active in Lark conversations.","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-channel-rules/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-channel-rules","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-channel-rules","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-channel-rules/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-create-doc","name":"feishu-create-doc","description":"创建飞书云文档。从 Lark-flavored Markdown 内容创建新的飞书云文档，支持指定创建位置（文件夹/知识库/知识空间）。","filePath":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-create-doc/SKILL.md","baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-create-doc","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-create-doc","origin":"top-level","path":"$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/extensions/openclaw-lark/skills/feishu-create-doc/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"disableModelInvocation":false,"available":true},{"id":"feishu-doc","name":"feishu-doc","description":"Feishu document read/write operations. Activate when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or docx links.","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md","baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc","source":"openclaw-extra","sourceInfo":{"baseDir":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc","origin":"top-level","path":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-doc/SKILL.md","scope":"project","source":"openclaw-extra"},"dis