1e\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 注意事项\n\n1. **GitHub master 分支**：被错误推送了 workspace 的内容，需要手动清理\n2. **虾评 changelog**：API 仍报 500 错误，建议后续反馈给虾评技术支持\n3. **MEMORY.md**：已更新 v4.8.4 发布记录\n\n---\n\n**🎉 v4.9.0/v4.8.4 发布完成！** 🍀"],"finalPromptText":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b501ebac884acb4a61d0879f5ba5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-30 09:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b501ebac884acb4a61d0879f5ba5]\nhaidong: 2，执行发布虾评和GitHub","itemLifecycle":{"startedCount":164,"completedCount":164,"activeCount":0},"toolMetas":[{"toolName":"write","meta":"to /tmp/changelog-v4.9.0.txt (582 chars)"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"stage git changes (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git add -A`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"create git commit (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git commit -m \"v4.9.0: Agent模式+CVE增强+文档完善 - 新增Agent模式(Python实现，兼容…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run git tag, `git tag -a v4.9.0 -m \"v4.9.0: 双模式兼容+CVE规则增强 P0 - Agent模式: - 解决脚本依赖问题 - 纯Python实现，兼容Coze/Dify/腾讯混元 - 支持基础扫描、规则解析、报告生成 P1…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"push git changes, `git push origin main`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run git remote → list git branches (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git remote -v && git branch -a`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"push git changes, `git push origin refs/heads/main`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"check git status → view git history, `git status && git log --oneline -1`"},{"toolName"