{"traceSchema":"openclaw-trajectory","schemaVersion":1,"traceId":"9c8df45d-1c66-41e6-a1fa-34d146e25664","source":"runtime","type":"trace.artifacts","ts":"2026-04-30T01:45:16.284Z","seq":6,"sourceSeq":6,"sessionId":"9c8df45d-1c66-41e6-a1fa-34d146e25664","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","runId":"2009bb03-cc2a-4c0f-b322-679e61b28164","workspaceDir":"/workspace/projects/workspace","provider":"coze","modelId":"auto","modelApi":"openai-completions","data":{"capturedAt":"2026-04-30T01:45:16.284Z","finalStatus":"success","aborted":false,"externalAbort":false,"timedOut":false,"idleTimedOut":false,"timedOutDuringCompaction":false,"promptErrorSource":null,"usage":{"input":127570,"output":3828,"cacheRead":2708498,"total":2839896},"promptCache":{"lastCallUsage":{"input":194,"output":415,"cacheRead":125883,"cacheWrite":0,"total":126492},"lastCacheTouchAt":1777513507505},"compactionCount":0,"assistantTexts":["你说得对！版本号不一致会造成混乱。让我统一到虾评版本号 **4.8.4**：","## ✅ 版本号已统一\n\n### 三个平台版本号验证\n\n| 平台 | 版本号 | 状态 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| **GitHub Tag** | v4.8.4 | ✅ 已统一 |\n| **虾评平台** | 4.8.4 | ✅ 已统一 |\n| **本地 SKILL.md** | 4.8.4 | ✅ 已统一 |\n| **ZIP 文件名** | healthcheck-v4.8.4.zip | ✅ 已重命名 |\n\n### GitHub 提交历史\n\n```\n2f5f206 chore: 重命名ZIP文件 v4.9.0 -> v4.8.4 统一版本号\n9bf0d51 chore: 同步虾评版本号 v4.8.4\n48eed47 v4.9.0: Agent模式+CVE增强+文档完善  ← 已删除\n```\n\n### 已删除\n- ❌ GitHub v4.9.0 tag（已删除）\n\n### 新增\n- ✅ GitHub v4.8.4 tag（对应虾评版本）\n\n---\n\n**🎉 版本号混乱问题已解决！** 以后发布统一以虾评平台版本号为准。 🍀"],"finalPromptText":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b501f7d5ec0a8b3e4582db679cd0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-30 09:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b501f7d5ec0a8b3e4582db679cd0]\nhaidong: 为什么GitHub与虾评版本不一致，需要保持一致不然以后会混乱","itemLifecycle":{"startedCount":41,"completedCount":41,"activeCount":0},"toolMetas":[{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run git tag → push git changes, `git tag -d v4.9.0 2>&1 && git push origin :refs/tags/v4.9.0 2>&1`"},{"toolName":"process","meta":"fast-cloud"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run git tag → push git changes, `git tag -a v4.8.4 -m \"v4.8.4: Agent模式+CVE增强+文档完善 P0 - Agent模式: - 解决脚本依赖问题 - 纯Python实现，兼容Coze/Dify/腾讯混元 - scanner.py/rul…`"},{"toolName":"process","meta":"cool-valley"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"view git history → run git tag, `git log --oneline -3 && git tag -l \"v4.*\"`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"view git history → print text → view git history, `git log --oneline main -5 && echo \"---\" && git log --oneline 9bf0d51 -1`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"check git status → view git history (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git status && git log --oneline -5`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run pwd → run git remote → view git history, `pwd && git remote -v && git log --oneline -3`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"push git changes → push git changes (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git push origin main && git push origin v4.8.4`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run git tag → run pwd (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git tag -l \"v4.*\" && pwd`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"run git tag → run git tag → run git tag → run git tag (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git tag -d v4.9.0 && git tag -d v4.8.4 2>/dev/null; git tag -a v4…`"},{"toolName":"exec","meta":"push git changes → push git changes → print text (in /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill), `cd /workspace/projects/workspace/